question.title: mise to setup java versions
question.body:
Hi I am using mise lib to manage & switch between different versions of java. I ran the command

mise use java@adoptopenjdk-8.0.402

A file .mise.toml was created with the following content.

[tools]
java = "adoptopenjdk-8.0.402"

Then I checked the java version. It still says java 17. I was expecting to see version 8.

I tried equivalent commands for python. I was able to switch between v3.11 and v3.12 seamlessly.

Is there any step that I am missing? TIA.
